snippet.title: NYSenate
snippet.description: This is the official channel of the NY State Senate. For the NY State Senate's Video Copyright Policy please visit http://www.nysenate.gov/copyright-policy . Note that the copyright policy and Rule XV of the NY State Senate Rules http://www.nysenate.gov/rules prohibit the use of televised proceedings, including any portion thereof, whether live or taped, for campaign or political purposes.
